                <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-white">The Kingdom Character</h1>
                <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-slate-200 mt-2 font-serif">A Sermon on the Mount (Enhanced with Gill & JFB)</p>
            </div>
